            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1052092051" class="vote-count">8</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1052092051" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1052092051">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/48563265/">一钟</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-06-20</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">图像历史纪实性小说？《茫茫黑夜漫游》既视感。五六万字吧，看完后脑子里有各种画面，各种声音，各种味道……</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1125723168">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1125723168" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1125723168" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1125723168">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/guanxia/">顾然</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-12-24</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">平平淡淡的回忆录，更多时候像是牢骚不断的老头子随口说出来的片段记忆，即使背景那么沉重也完全没有啥感觉来着，三星半。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1075268989">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1075268989" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1075268989" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1075268989">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
