                    <span>2016-10-11</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">文字部分比较好，绘画缺看点</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1056235689">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1056235689" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1056235689" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1056235689">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/savage1Q88/">雏田</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-08-09</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">虽然是一本漫画书，但是文字量还是很大。讲述战争中发生的被人遗忘或者忽略的细节。也是“笑中带泪”，最重要的是画风。大篇幅的画稿特别多！</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1053642464">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1053642464" class="vote-count">2</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1053642464" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1053642464">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/hinabook/">后浪</a>
                    <span>2016-07-18</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">尤擅掌控战争题材的当代漫画大师塔蒂首次触碰“二战”，
动员全家人鼓起勇气直面惨痛的家族历史。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

